    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car, and honestly, it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It drives smoothly and looks great, making it the perfect pick if you want something dependable without breaking the bank. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to a good home. Come take it for a test drive and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
